# Security response headers.
# NOTE: Appwrite Sites' static adapter may not read this file; if these headers
# don't appear in production, configure them on the Site in the Appwrite console.
# Conservative set only — no strict CSP, to avoid breaking Emotion/MUI inline styles.
/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()
